terra.shell.logging

Class LogManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • terra.shell.logging.LogManager

  • public class LogManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Resource class used to manage all Loggers registered with it, including all Loggers affiliated with the JProcess class. Generally LogManager should not be used directly as it may interfere with outputs of other processes.
    Author:
    dan
